	DeselectFlash:
		MGS5 A 0 A_JumpIfInventory("PB_HighCalMag", 14, 5)
		MGS4 A 0 A_JumpIfInventory("PB_HighCalMag", 12, 4)
		MGS3 A 0 A_JumpIfInventory("PB_HighCalMag", 10, 3)
